155.description:
{Slava's Ring of Power}

Gives Commander all six Primary Skills at Advanced level.

To give this artifact to your Commander, drag it to the Commander icon.

156.description:
{Warlord's Banner}

With stack experience enabled, the Warlord's Banner gives additional bonuses in combat. To equip it, drag it to the troop stack of your choice.

Choose a bonus by right-clicking on the Banner in the stack's experience screen. You can change the bonus any time except in combat.

159.description:
{Dragonheart}

This ancient relic summons up to [100 HP x Hero Level] dragons for the duration of a battle (minimum one dragon). Dragon type is random but may be influenced by terrain.

In addition, dragons in a hero's army always have positive morale.

160.description:
{Gate Key}

Upon entering a town you own, the Gate Key gives you the option to lock it for 5 days. Heroes can leave locked towns but no hero can enter except by Town Portal or Castle Gate, and the town cannot be attacked.

The Gate Key will vanish when used and returns to the hero 10 days later. A town cannot be relocked by any Gate Key for 5 days after it becomes unlocked. If a player is vanquished, their locked towns will be unlocked for all players the following day.
